section: ghc-lib
synopsis: GHC API changes for diagnostic related locations
issues: #22637
mrs: !16100

description: {
In support of related locations in diagnostics:

- The ``Diagnostic`` class gains a method ``diagnosticRelatedLocations ::
  a -> [SrcSpan]``, with a default implementation returning ``[]``.
- The ``MCDiagnostic`` constructor of ``MessageClass`` carries an additional
  ``[SrcSpan]`` field with the related locations.
- ``getCaretDiagnostic`` is replaced by ``getCaretDiagnostics``, which
  renders carets for multiple spans and returns the real spans that did not
  receive one.
- The ``TcRnDuplicateExport`` and ``TcRnDuplicateNamedDefaultExport``
  constructors of ``TcRnMessage`` now carry located export items
  (``LIE GhcPs`` instead of ``IE GhcPs``).
}
